news.title: West Nile vaccine to enter clinical trial
news.summary: Stephen Feller BETHESDA, Md., July 6 (UPI) -- The NIH announced a clinical trial to test the safety of a West Nile vaccine in humans that protected mice from lethal doses of the virus in lab tests.
